    BG/NBD (Fader, Hardie, and Lee 2005 <doi:10.1287/mksc.1040.0098>) and 
    Pareto/NBD and Gamma/Gamma (Fader, Hardie, and Lee 2005 <doi:10.1509/jmkr.2005.42.4.415>) models.
